<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">The Broken Status Quo</div>
    <h2>
      The companies still building infrastructure from scratch won't be around
      to see patients.
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="problem-grid">
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <h3>You've been at this for over a year — and you still don't have a live patient</h3>
      <p>
        Your team is talented. Your care model is strong. But you're still
        hiring DevOps engineers, security architects, and compliance officers —
        building the foundation, not the product. Not a single line of care code
        written.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <h3>Every audit finding is a threat you didn't see coming</h3>
      <p>
        HIPAA, SOC 2, state-level regulations — you're navigating them with
        internal teams or expensive consultants, constantly bracing for the
        finding that derails your timeline. And the regulatory surface area
        keeps growing.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-card reveal">
      <h3>Every month you wait, your competitor pulls further ahead</h3>
      <p>
        While you're building infrastructure that has nothing to do with patient
        care, AI-native companies are automating scheduling, intake, and routing
        — seeing patients, generating revenue, and compounding their lead. That
        gap doesn't close. It widens every month you wait.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: 8rem 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .problem h2 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--slate));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.4s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .problem-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.4),
      transparent
    );
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .problem {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
